    bibo:volume "236" ;
    dc:creator "Treher Eberly, Amanda; Naczi, Robert F. C." ;
    dc:date "2023" ;
    dc:title "Rhynchospora mesoatlantica (Cyperaceae), an imperiled new species of beaksedge from eastern U. S. A." ;
    fabio:hasPart <http://dx.doi.org/10.3897/phytokeys.236.111271.figure2>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.3897/phytokeys.236.111271.figure3>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.3897/phytokeys.236.111271.figure4>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.3897/phytokeys.236.111271.figure5>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.3897/phytokeys.236.111271.figure6> ;
    a fabio:JournalArticle .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.3897/phytokeys.236.111271.figure2>
    dc:description "Figure 2. Representative mature fruits of Rhynchospora species. Left to right: Rhynchospora filifolia [Naczi 12060 A & Treher (NY)], R. harperi [Naczi 16347 (NY)], and R. mesoatlantica [Naczi 12060 & Treher (NY)]. Scale bar: 1.0 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/945902" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.3897/phytokeys.236.111271.figure3>
    dc:description "Figure 3. Rhynchospora mesoatlantica A habit B distal portion of infructescence C spikelet D distal scale E immature fruit F mature fruit, lateral view, with detail of perianth bristle (left) and top view (below). From Treher 84 & Naczi (Holotype, NY). Scale bars: 2 cm (A); 1 cm (B); 1 mm (C, D, E); 0.5 mm (F)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/945903" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.3897/phytokeys.236.111271.figure4>
    dc:description "Figure 4. Habit of Rhynchospora mesoatlantica. Amanda T. Eberly with R. mesoatlantica rooted in habitat at type locality (Treher 84 & Naczi)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/945904" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.3897/phytokeys.236.111271.figure5>
    dc:description "Figure 5. Known geographic distribution of Rhynchospora mesoatlantica. Based on all known collections." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/945905" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.3897/phytokeys.236.111271.figure6>
    dc:description "Figure 6. Representative habitat of Rhynchospora mesoatlantica. At type locality (Treher 84 & Naczi)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/945906" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

